      "message": "Good point, and actually that\u0027s the point I was wondering.\n\nI considered checking manual attributes in testing.Test validation, but since attribute validation should be done against a complete set of attributes (rather than checking testing.Test.Attr and testing.Param.Attr separately), let me check it in newTestInstance.",
